Class MatrixSub

java.lang.Object
  MatrixSub
public class MatrixSub
extends java.lang.Object

Matrix substitution used for alignment : transition/transversion matrix for Nucleic Acid ; identity matrix or Blosum50 matrix for Amino-Acids. To know if a sequence is Proteic or Nucleic see in LifeSequence.

Author:
Gabriel Chandesris
See Also:
LifeSequence.getSeqType(java.lang.String)
